Revision history for DBIO-MySQL

{{$NEXT}}
    - Initial release as standalone distribution extracted from DBIO core
    - DBIO::MySQL schema component and DBIO::MySQL::Storage driver
    - DBIO::MySQL::MariaDB schema component and DBIO::MySQL::Storage::MariaDB driver
    - DBIO::MySQL::SQLMaker with MySQL-specific SQL generation
    - DBIO::MySQL::Loader for Schema::Loader MySQL introspection support
    - Add DBD::mysql as explicit dependency
    - Migrate test suite from DBICTest to DBIO::Test
    - Rename all DBIC references to DBIO throughout
    - Rename _dbic_connect_attributes to _dbio_connect_attributes
    - Replace Path::Class with DBIO::Util path helpers in Loader
    - Add replicated coverage to MySQL driver tests
    - Comprehensive POD documentation for all modules
    - Align POD with DBIO conventions (=attr, =method collectors)
    - Restore historical Loader provenance note
